task.summary: 1st Commit. This is Shreya's original source code.
Adding intelij project file and maven pom.xml
Added refactored stopWords into StopWordFilter and made a test for it. I will have Greg reimplement this with a set, instead of a long chain of boolean statements.
Revamped. Added TODOs. Note: having trouble with refactoring and committing.
Created WekaSMOClassifier and WekaSMOClassifierFactory to handle building SMO Classifier and predictions/evaluations on a new testing set. Respective changes made in Prediction
Reformatted Prediction. Use with load() and run()
Condensed StopWordFilter, ManageMappings, and preprocessDoc into one class: Preprocessing
Added new Training class (kept the old as a reference)
Eliminated Stem class - stem() method fused with Preprocessor
LSA + Training finished. Generated and added Ant build
Upgraded Training algorithm to build and save the term by document matrix all in one shot. Runs way faster now.
Minor changes to LSA + Training. Build now features ant train, lsa, and predict.
Minor changes to LSA + Prediction + Training
minor fix to QAPair, reformatting of cotraining
